nodes.text: D435 was a G1 series equipment operator droid that worked for the Tredway family in the mines of the Sil'Lume asteroid belt. It saved Dena Tredway shortly after Imperial Governor Sebastian Parnell destroyed the asteroid base. After Dena was delivered to Luke Skywalker for transport to Ire Eleazari's asteroid, D435 deactivated itself to avoid Imperial capture.
